==Awards==
* [[Iron Cross]] (1939)
** 2nd Class (21 September 1939){{sfn|Thomas|1997|p=208}}
** 1st Class (13 June 1940){{sfn|Thomas|1997|p=208}}
* [[Narvik Shield]] (30 January 1941)<ref>{{Cite web |website=Hermann Historica |title=Deutsche Zeitgeschichte, Orden und Militaria ab 1919—Los Nr. 7263 |url=http://www.hermann-historica.de/auktion/hhm64.pl?f=NR_LOT&c=7263&t=temartic_R_D&db=kat64_3R.txt |language=German |accessdate=5 October 2015}}</ref>
* [[Front Flying Clasp of the Luftwaffe]] in Gold (11 May 1941)<ref>{{Cite web |website=Hermann Historica |title=Deutsche Zeitgeschichte, Orden und Militaria ab 1919—Los Nr. 7262 |url=http://www.hermann-historica.de/auktion/hhm64.pl?f=NR_LOT&c=7262&t=temartic_R_D&db=kat64_3R.txt |language=German |accessdate=5 October 2015}}</ref>
* ''[[Ehrenpokal der Luftwaffe]]'' (21 July 1941){{sfn|Obermaier|1989|p=19}}
* [[Combined Pilots-Observation Badge]] in Gold with Diamonds{{sfn|Berger|1999|p=86}}
* [[Knight's Cross of the Iron Cross with Oak Leaves, Swords and Diamonds]]
** Knight's Cross on 18 September 1941 as ''[[Hauptmann]]'' and ''[[Gruppenkommandeur]]'' of II./''Jagdgeschwader'' 3{{sfn|Scherzer|2007|p=341}}{{sfn|Fellgiebel|2000|p=199}}{{sfn|Von Seemen|1976|p=143}}
** 38th Oak Leaves on 26 October 1941 as ''Hauptmann'' and ''Gruppenkommandeur'' of II./''Jagdgeschwader'' 3{{sfn|Fellgiebel|2000|p=55}}{{sfn|Von Seemen|1976|p=26}}{{refn|According to German author Veit Scherzer on 25 October 1941.{{sfn|Scherzer|2007|p=341}}|group="Note"}}
** 13th Swords on 23 June 1942 as ''Hauptmann'' and ''[[Geschwaderkommodore]]'' of ''Jagdgeschwader'' 77{{sfn|Scherzer|2007|p=341}}{{sfn|Fellgiebel|2000|p=40}}{{sfn|Von Seemen|1976|p=14}}
** 3rd Diamonds on 30 August 1942 as ''[[Major (Germany)|Major]]'' and ''Geschwaderkommodore'' of ''Jagdgeschwader'' 77{{sfn|Scherzer|2007|p=341}}{{sfn|Fellgiebel|2000|p=36}}{{sfn|Von Seemen|1976|p=12}}
* Mentioned three times in the ''[[Wehrmachtbericht]]'' (25 October 1941, 20 June 1942 and 31 August 1942)
* [[Crimea Shield]] (15 March 1943)<ref>{{Cite web |website=Hermann Historica |title=Deutsche Zeitgeschichte, Orden und Militaria ab 1919—Los Nr. 7264 |url=http://www.hermann-historica.de/auktion/hhm64.pl?f=NR_LOT&c=7264&t=temartic_R_D&db=kat64_3R.txt |language=German |accessdate=5 October 2015}}</ref>

